queries.sql: SELECT m.*,r.* FROM app_menu m LEFT JOIN app_role r ON r.menu_id = m.menu_id LEFT JOIN app_group g ON r.group_id = g.group_id WHERE r.group_id='4' AND m.deleted_at IS NULL AND m.aktif='1' AND r.akses_lihat='1' ORDER BY urutan ASC;
SELECT m.*,r.* FROM app_menu m LEFT JOIN app_role r ON r.menu_id = m.menu_id LEFT JOIN app_group g ON r.group_id = g.group_id WHERE m.prefik='capaian-skp' ;

SELECT sskp.periode_id, prd.periode_awal, prd.periode_akhir FROM susunan_skp sskp INNER JOIN link_hirarki link ON sskp.nip = link.nip INNER JOIN periode_skp prd ON prd.periode_id = sskp.periode_id WHERE link.link_atasan_id = '197707051997031003' AND prd.is_default='Ya' GROUP BY prd.periode_awal, prd.periode_akhir ORDER BY prd.periode_akhir DESC;

SELECT periode.nip,periode.nama FROM susunan_skp skp INNER JOIN periode_skp periode ON skp.periode_id = periode.periode_id WHERE periode.is_default='Ya' AND skp.nip IN (SELECT link.nip FROM link_hirarki link WHERE link.link_atasan_id='197707051997031003' AND deleted_at IS NULL) GROUP BY periode.nip

SELECT skp.* FROM susunan_skp skp INNER JOIN periode_skp periode ON skp.periode_id = periode.periode_id WHERE periode.nip='198609232010011008' AND periode.is_default='Ya' AND skp.nip IN (SELECT link.nip FROM link_hirarki link WHERE link.link_atasan_id='197707051997031003' AND deleted_at IS NULL) ;
